    "Statistical analysisStatistical analyses were performed using Python.",
    "ANOVA and Tukey's HSD tests were used to compare character count differences in responses among the three LLM-Chatbots and human doctors, as the data met parametric criteria.",
    "Kruskal Wallis and Dunn's post-hoc tests assessed differences in word counts and comprehensiveness scores between the LLMs and human doctors.",
    "Pearson's χ2 test was applied to compare rating proportions ('Poor', 'Borderline', 'Good', 'Very Good') within the LLM chatbots.",
    "Bonferroni correction was applied for multiple hypothesis testing, with p-values < 0.05 deemed signi cant."
